ğŸ”¹ Prompt Engineering vs Context Engineering
Prompt Engineering: Creating clear and effective prompts to get the best AI response.
 Context Engineering: Giving background or extra info so AI fully understands the situation.
 Difference: Prompt focuses on question quality, context focuses on information clarity.
ğŸ”¹ How They Work Together
Prompt tells what to do, and context tells why and how.
 Together, they make AI replies more accurate, relevant, and human-like.
 Good prompt + good context = best AI performance.
ğŸ”¹ Temperature & Top-p
Temperature: Controls creativity (low = focused, high = creative).
 Top-p: Chooses words based on probability for balanced responses.
