It sets AIâ€™s role or behavior (e.g., â€œYou are a teacherâ€ or â€œYou are a doctorâ€).
 Defines style, tone, and focus of all replies.
ğŸ”¹ Role Prompting
Tells AI what identity to take â€” makes replies more realistic and context-aware.
ğŸ”¹ Contextual Prompting
Adds relevant background or user info so AI gives personalized and accurate answers.


